  "texts": [
    "The voxels surrounding each query point are used to interpolate and calculate its value.",
    "As a result, rendering new 2D views is accomplished without the need for a neural network, considerably reducing complexity and computational demands.",
    "Plenoxels are two orders of magnitude faster than NeRF and offer a similar visual quality.",
    "Inverse rendering is applied using the original NeRF in Instant-NeRF (Jonathan 2022; Isha 2022), which was made available by NVIDIA.",
    "The integration of AI with AR has the potential to revolutionize the way we interact with the Metaverse by enabling more natural and intuitive experiences."
  ],
